dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Langlade County, Wisconsin in 2022. [A road layer constructed like many using segments with ranges of numbers between for emergency management purposes. There are over 3000 segments in Langlade County. Some of the roads which are kept track of are Private and marked accordingly in a field or annotation. Maintenance and Update Frequency: Updated at least quarterly.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
